# Keep the Docker build context tiny. The image Dockerfiles only COPY the wrapper
# scripts (.devcontainer/build) and the firewall scripts (.devcontainer/claude-code);
# exclude all pipeline data/output + VCS so `docker build .` ships ~KBs, not GBs.
.git
.github
runs/
cloneval/
nf_input/
work/
**/work/
*.sif
*.img
# Match data/artifacts at ANY depth, not just the context root: a bare `*.fastq.gz`
# in .dockerignore does NOT match nested paths, so real-data dirs (e.g.
# MT260625_*_fastq_pass/barcodeNN/*.fastq.gz) would otherwise ship in the build context.
**/*.sif
**/*.img
**/*.fastq
**/*.fastq.gz
**/*.fq
**/*.fq.gz
**/*_fastq_pass/
examples/
arabidopsis_db/
